1) If you want to use H2-DB
    ==>first add h2 database dependency
    then inside the application.properties file 
    ==>spring.datasource.url=jdbc:h2:mem:testdb
       spring.datasource.driverClassName=org.h2.Driver
       spring.datasource.username=sa
       spring.datasource.password=password
       spring.jpa.database-platform=org.hibernate.dialect.H2Dialect
    ==> after that check url and username
       or copy url from application.properties file and paste 
       of h2-console url
       write down the password make connection.
       *** If you don't change that url it will show username or password is incorrect
       
